title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Heinkel He 162 Salamander  -version 09h
description:
In this video we will look at the Heinkel He 162 salamander  which received it first update. After we looked at the exterior we start the engines and will taxi to the runway and see how the power adjustments are working ;-)

If you also want to give this aircraft a try download your own copy from:
https://flightsim.to/file/22906/native-project-heinkel-he-162-salamander
